---
layout: base.njk
title: "Trace Your Family's Footsteps — Heroes and Heritage Tours"
description: "Send us your relative's name and we'll research their service record and battlefield locations, then build it into your tour — so you can stand where they stood."
activeNav: family-research
permalink: "/family-research.html"
---

<header class="hero hero--compact">
  <div class="hero-media">
    <img src="{{ familyResearch.heroImage }}" alt="{{ familyResearch.heroAlt }}" width="1800" height="1200">
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">A tour like no other</span>
      <h1>Trace your family's footsteps.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Give us a name, and we'll help you find the ground they stood on. It has been, for many of our families, the most meaningful day of their trip.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" data-reveal>
      <div class="stack" style="gap: var(--space-3);">
        <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
        <h2>From a name in your family tree, to a place you can stand.</h2>
        {% for p in familyResearch.introParagraphs %}
        <p class="body-text">{{ p }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-photo">
        <img src="{{ familyResearch.sideImage }}" alt="{{ familyResearch.sideImageAlt }}" width="1800" height="1350">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-list" style="margin-top: var(--space-7); max-width: 900px; margin-inline: auto;" data-reveal>
      {% for step in familyResearch.steps %}
      <div class="feature-row">
        <div class="icon-circle" style="background: var(--red);"><span style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px;">{{ loop.index }}</span></div>
        <div class="feature-row-text">
          <h4>{{ step.title }}</h4>
          <p>{{ step.text }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center on-dark" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--on-dark">Real family stories</span>
      <h2>What families have found.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-grid" data-reveal>
      {% for t in testimonials %}
        {% if t.name in familyResearch.storyTestimonials %}
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <span class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</span>
          <blockquote>{{ t.quote }}</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-attribution">
            {% if t.photo %}<img src="{{ t.photo }}" alt="{{ t.name }}" loading="lazy">{% else %}<div class="testimonial-avatar-fallback">{{ t.name | initials }}</div>{% endif %}
            <div class="testimonial-attribution-text"><strong>{{ t.name }}</strong><span>{{ t.role }}</span></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2>Ready to find their footsteps?</h2>
      <p class="lede">Book any tour and add your family research request in the notes — or contact us first if you'd like to talk it through.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/booking.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book a Tour</a>
        <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" style="border-color: rgba(244,238,225,0.4); color: #FFF;">Tell Us Their Story First</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
